info.name: Nature Background Roblox Theme
info.description:
NEW DLC https://userstyles.org/styles/169024 

Lets most of roblox become transparent and see through with an amazing picture as the background. There will be a lot of updates so make sure you keep it updated! Some parts are hard to read and - sorry.
info.additionalInfo:
This took me forever so please install to show support. I will be updating it so it can be easier to read. I will also occasionally being changing the background image. If you have any questions or suggestions either message me on roblox or on Discord at Matthewxyz#7937.
